flowchart TD
    A[Admin opens certificate area] --> B[Select student and certificate type]
    B --> C[Click Generate Certificate]
    C --> D[Validate student eligibility]
    D --> E{Eligible?}
    E -->|No| F[Show not eligible message]
    E -->|Yes| G[Generate certificate file]
    G --> H{Generation success?}
    H -->|No| I[Show generation error]
    H -->|Yes| J[Store certificate record]
    J --> K[Store version and file reference]
    K --> L[Trigger certificate created email if enabled]
    L --> M[Student opens certificate page]
    M --> N[Student downloads certificate]